%section#wildlife.container.content-section
  .row
    .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
      %h2.text-center Wildlife
      %p
        \The particular habitat of undisturbed wooded savannah and rainforest in
        \the Chinko/Mbari drainage basin allows for an incredible richness of
        \species, and puzzling phenomena, making it a hotspot of biodiversity.

      %p
        .image
          = image_tag('wildlife/wild-dog-family.jpg', class: 'img-responsive')
          .image-description
            Wild Dog Family

      %p
        \The Chinko Project research division has documented the many species present
        \(mammals and birds), with more than a hundred thousand camera trapping pictures
        \that allow for a rare glimpse into the beauty of the areaâ€™s flora and fauna.

      %p
        Explore a selection of these pictures together with our publications online at our
        = succeed '.' do
          = link_to "research platform", "http://research.chinkoproject.com", { target: '_blank' }

      #wildlife-carousel.owl-carousel
        - %w(oribi-in-savannah-opening warthog leopard-track leopard leopard-in-front-of-camera-trap hartebeest).each do |name|
          .image
            = image_tag('wildlife/'+ name +'.jpg')
            .image-description
              = name.titleize

      :javascript
        $(document).ready(function(){
          $("#wildlife-carousel").owlCarousel({
              items: 1,
              loop: true,
              margin: 10,
              lazyLoad: true,
              merge: true,
              video: true
            });
        });
